s|TAG_BIO_2008_LATEST_NEWS|<b>Shilpa Shetty Receives Invitation From Michael Jackson</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Sonam Kapoor New Face Of L’Oreal" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/12_22_2008.html">12/26/2008</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> has received an invitation from king of pop Michael Jackson to attend his brothers Jermaine Jackson's birthday party. Shilpa and Jermaine Jackson had taken part in international reality show Big Brother, where Shilpa had ended up winning.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Shilpa Shetty To Host Season 2 Of Big Boss</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty To Host Season 2 Of Big Boss" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/08_04_2008.html">08/07/2008</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> the winner of the Big Brother UK, will be the host of <A ALT="" TITLE="Bigg Boss 2" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/tv_shows/bigg_boss/bigg_boss.html">Bigg Boss 2</A> Indian version of the show. The show will star to air on TV on August 17, it will also make it the first reality show to be telecast on all seven days of the week. The show is have 14 people locked into a house under the surveillance of over 30 cameras for a period of three months.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Shilpa Shetty Could Host Season 2 Of Big Boss</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty Could Host Season 2 Of Big Boss" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/07_28_2008.html">07/28/2008</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> the winner of the Big Brother UK, may be offered to host the next season of <A ALT="" TITLE="Bigg Boss 2" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/tv_shows/bigg_boss/bigg_boss.html">Bigg Boss 2</A> in India. Bigg Boss was last year hosted by Arshad Warsi. If Shilpa chooses to host the show, she could be paid more then Rs 8 Crores. Bigg Boss (India) will start after <A ALT="" TITLE="Fear Factor Khatron Ke Khiladi" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/tv_shows/fear_factor_khatron_ke_khiladi/fear_factor_khatron_ke_khiladi.html">Fear Factor Khatron Ke Khiladi</A>, , hosted by <A ALT="" TITLE="Akshay Kumar" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/akshay_kumar/bollywood_akshay_kumar.html">Akshay Kumar</A> , ends in August 2008. The new season of Bigg Boss will air on newly launched channel, Colors.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Shilpa Shetty Turns Producer</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty Turns Producer" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/07_07_2008.html">07/09/2008</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> has turned into an entrepreneur by setting up her won production company named, Shilpa Shetty Global Productions. The first movie to be produced by the new production house will be the film named <A ALT="" TITLE="VIP Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2008/vip.html">VIP (2008)</A> , which will also be co produced by UTV Motion Pictures and directed by Manish Jha. The movie will star Shilpa herself, along with <A ALT="" TITLE="Bipasha Basu" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/bipasha_basu/bollywood_bipasha_basu.html">Bipasha Basu</A>. While Shilpa’s sister, <A ALT="" TITLE="Shamita Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shamita_shetty/bollywood_shamita_shetty.html">Shamita Shetty</A> , will not be seen on the screen in the movie but will play key role behind the scene as she is the creative producer for the film.<br><hr size="1" width="100%">  <b>Shilpa Shetty Wins Global Diversity Award 2008</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty Wins Global Diversity Award 2008" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/07_07_2008.html">07/07/2008</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> has become very popular oversee after her appearance and later wining on Channel 4's reality TV show Celebrity Big Brother in 2007. She was recently given the Global diversity Award 2008 in London for her significant contribution to the public appreciation and understanding of diversity. Shilpa also helped the organizer raise over 63,000 pounds for the the Silver Star Appeal charity.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Shilpa Shetty On The Cover Of Cosmopolitan</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty On The Cover Of Cosmopolitan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/06_16_2008.html">06/16/2008</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> gave a great phoot to Cosmopolitan for the June 2008 edition of the magazine. Shilpa become world famous after winning the Big Brother UK last year. Shilpa has the perfect silm body with nice long silky hair, curvaceous body, a great smile and the nice height. Shilpa next will be seeing in a item number song in the movie <A ALT="" TITLE="Dostana Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2008/dostana.html">Dostana (2008)</A>.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Shilpa Shetty Launches Yoga DVD</b> <br> <font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty Yoga DVD" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/01_07_2008.html">01/11/2008</A>: </font> <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> launched a new DVD titled Shilpa's Yoga. The DVD is tragted to the European market, where she has been popular since winning the Bigg Boss TV show. The DV