s|TAG_BIO_2007_LATEST_NEWS|<b>Shilpa Shetty Dating Raj Kundra</b> <br> <font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty Dating Raj Kundra" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2007/12_31_2007.html">12/31/2007</A>: </font> <br> It has been reported that Bollywood movie star <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> is dating Raj Kundra, London-based businessman. Raj is also the person behind the launch of Shilpa's perfume S2 and a yoga DVD. Only time will tell if this is ture and if Shilpa is ready for marriage.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Bollywood Stars Win Rajiv Gandhi Award</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2007/08_13_2007.html">08/13/2007</A> <br> Bollywood star <A ALT="" TITLE="Salman Khan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/salman_khan/bollywood_salman_khan.html">Salman Khan</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> won the Rajiv Gandhi award along with journalist Shekhar Gupta and Indian-American astronaut Sunita Williams. The awards were presented by Sushilkumar Shinde and Maharashtra Chief Minister Vilasrao Deshmukh. Others winners include Veerendra Heggade, D Y Patil, Swati Piramal, Sir Gulam Noon, Khushagra Bajaj, Tulsi Tanti, and Pooja Bhangira.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Shilpa Shetty In Sydney and Melbourne</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bollywood Movie News" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2007/05_07_2007.html">05/11/2007</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> recently visited Sydney, Australia and Melbourne, Australia to promote her movie Life in a <A ALT="" TITLE="Metro Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2007/metro.html">Metro (2007)</A> . She was only in the town for a couple of days but had a packed schedule with many face to face interviews and photo shoots. Due to her recent win on the UK show Big Brother she has gained international appeal.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Shilpa Shetty Meets Queen Elizabeth II</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bollywood Movie News" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2007/03_12_2007.html">03/15/2007</A>: <br> In the last couple of month, <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> has become well known in UK, first she won the Celebrity Big Brother title and now she is meeting up with Queen Elizabeth II. The meeting took place at a Commonwealth Day event in London, during which Shilpa was a guest speakers. During the speech, she talked about racism and AIDS.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Shilpa Shetty Wins Big Brother Title</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bollywood Movie News" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2007/01_29_2007.html">01/29/2007</A> <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> won the title of on the reality show Celebrity Big Brother (UK) beating out Michael Jackson's big brother Jermaine Jackson on Sunday Jan 28, 2007. She was paid more then 40,000 pounds for her participation. Also back in India, Rahul Roy was crowned the winner of Bigg Boss (India).<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Shilpa Shetty Offended On British reality TV?</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bollywood Movie News" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2007/01_15_2007.html">01/17/2007</A> <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shilpa Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shilpa_shetty/bollywood_shilpa_shetty.html">Shilpa Shetty</A> has been signed by the British reality TV to be on the popular show Celebrity Big Brother and has 